Titolo: Deadfall Adventures

Anno: 2013

Descrizione: Deadfall Adventures is an action-adventure video game developed by The Farm 51 and published by Nordic Games. Deadfall Adventures was released on November 15, 2013, for Windows and Xbox 360, and on October 28, 2014, for PlayStation 3. The game is set in the universe of the Allan Quatermain series, created by H. Rider Haggard.